notes:
**Note 1:** Record the interpretation for the highest PSA lab value recorded in the medical record prior to diagnostic biopsy of prostate and treatment.   This lab value may be recorded in the lab report, history and physical, or clinical statement in the pathology report. 

**Note 2:**  The interpretation should be for the same laboratory test recorded in **Site-Specific Factor 1, Prostatic Specific Antigen (PSA) Lab Value**.
